                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 837.00/517.</note>
                        <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-12-14">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">December</hi> 14, 1911</date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>The Senate amendment removing the exception of the judiciary from
                            dismissal has been accepted and the amended bill goes to the President
                            for signature.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Gibson</hi>.</signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
